<L>__{exterior london street day bus stop}
<A>__{in another part of town. the camera is on the crowd of fifteen or twenty people waiting for the bus. when the bus pulls up, they all crowd in. the camera goes to floor level and slowly examines the footwear of the crowded bus. passengers are standing in the aisle and the camera slowly pans on their galoshes, boots, high heels, rubbers, etc., until it comes to rest on a conspicuous pair of bare feet. we pan up to find david clad only in a woman's rain coat with a fur collar trying to look as nonchalant as possible. a man looks at him oddly.}
